      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING DELORIS (2) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (17.63) at Taree Super Track. Can measure up this time. BARRAMUNDI LOU (1) jumped well and was in the mix early before fading out of it late when 6th over 400m at this track in Free For All company. Solid record here at the distance winning 12 races. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. STYLISH ROBBO (7) has a strong record this track and trip with 24 wins and 15 placings from 50 starts. Placed last time (22.72) at this track in a NG, finishing second and beaten 2.25 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. STAR (8) is always hard to beat when she races here at this trip.",
